description: A search is reported for low-mass structures in the $\mathrm{J}/\psi\mathrm{J}/\psi$ mass spectrum produced by proton-proton collisions at $\sqrt{s} = 13\,\mathrm{TeV}$. The data sample corresponds to an integrated luminosity of 135 fb$^{-1}$ collected by the CMS experiment at the LHC.
